column2: SELECT TOP # zns.nvote, zns.ra, zns.dec, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger FROM SpecObjAll as G JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON G.targetObjID = zns.objid WHERE zns.nvote >= # and zns.p_cw > # and zns.p_mg > #
